data.description: This is a vacant lot. Account R340366.  1S3E16CD 3000.  Located in the Gresham Butte neighborhood in Gresham, Multnomah County, Oregon.  The elevation is 630'.  Property taxes are $1,244.29 per year (2020).  It is likely a difficult lot to develop and may be best utilized with an adjoining property. The property has an access easement.  It appears to have a small portion of frontage along the road but it's not certain.
